################################################################
#                                                              #
#   DMA Round-Robin Arbitration Verification Testbench        #
#   Module Under Test: dma_arbiter (inside tlul_dma)          #
#                                                              #
#   Arbitration Policy: Round-Robin per-word fairness         #
#   When both channels request bus access, grants alternate    #
#   between CH0 and CH1 on every word transfer (READ+WRITE).  #
#                                                              #
#   Test Plan:                                                #
#     TC1: Equal Simultaneous   (CH0=4, CH1=4 words)          #
#     TC2: Unequal Concurrent   (CH0=8, CH1=4 words)          #
#     TC3: Staggered Start      (CH0 head start, then CH1)    #
#     TC4: Single Channel       (CH1 only, 4 words)           #
#     TC5: Restart During Run   (CH0 done+restart w/ CH1)     #
#                                                              #
#   Verification Metrics:                                     #
#     - Per-channel grant counts                              #
#     - Strict alternation in overlap window                  #
#     - Max imbalance (fairness bound)                        #
#     - Destination data integrity                            #
#                                                              #
################################################################
# 
# 
